      "text": "A 40-year-old man is brought to therapy by his partner, who is frustrated with his constant need for admiration and his belief that he deserves special treatment. He frequently exaggerates his achievements and often feels that others are envious of him. Which type of personality disorder is he most likely exhibiting?",
